<!-- Button trigger modal -->
<button type="button" class="btn mr-1 px-2 py-1" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#buffedDropsModal">
<i class="bi bi-question-circle"></i>
</button>

<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal" id="buffedDropsModal" tabindex="-1">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5">Enemy drops are buffed</h1>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
      <p>If enabled, then certain enemy drops are improved:
      <ul>
      <li>Small energy drops give 10 energy.
      <li>Respawning enemies drop Power Bombs at double the normal rate.
      </ul>
      </p>

      <h5>Details</h5>
      <p>
      The enemies with improved Power Bomb drop rate are Gamets, Zebs, Geegas, Zebbos, Zoas, and Coverns.
      Drop rates of enemy projectiles are not affected. The increased Power Bomb drop rate comes out of the
      Missile drop rate. The resulting drop rates are shown in the following table:

      <table class="table w-auto table-striped table-bordered mx-auto">
      <thead>
        <tr>
        <th scope="col">Enemy</th>
        <th scope="col">Nothing</th>
        <th scope="col">Small Energy</th>
        <th scope="col">Large Energy</th>
        <th scope="col">Missile</th>
        <th scope="col">Super</th>
        <th scope="col">Power Bomb</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
          <tr><td>Gamet</td><td>2%</td><td>24%</td><td>24%</td><td>20%</td><td>24%</td><td>8%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Zeb</td><td>2%</td><td>24%</td><td>24%</td><td>20%</td><td>24%</td><td>8%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Geega</td><td>2%</td><td>24%</td><td>24%</td><td>20%</td><td>24%</td><td>8%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Zebbo</td><td>0%</td><td>0%</td><td>56%</td><td>2%</td><td>40%</td><td>4%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Zoa</td><td>2%</td><td>0%</td><td>40%</td><td>24%</td><td>28%</td><td>8%</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Covern</td><td>0%</td><td>20%</td><td>38%</td><td>20%</td><td>8%</td><td>16%</td></tr>
      </tbody>
      </table>
  
      </p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
